{"id":"2f2e1212-8278-4628-8e89-47d6f9b139e8","name":"Re: Zero","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">The World of </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 137, 197)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">Re:Zero</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">, you take on </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(162, 221, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">Subaru Natsuki's</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\"> place as the summoned one.You all know what happens here in </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 98, 146)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">ReZero</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">, this could either be very bad or very good, you decide.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">Currently I'm only entering information for the, it is currently up to </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 74, 207)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">Arc 5</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 198, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61); color: inherit\">, I'll continue it later, for sure.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 66, 66); color: inherit\">Arch 5 is now available</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">(<em>I didn't think I could get hooked on developing this, I suppose</em>)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 242, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(77, 77, 77); color: inherit\">Enjoy!!!</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>[[I add the appearances, I suppose.]]</strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"1a6887ec-ab22-4ebe-83c9-119477db2399_36adead5-3a9c-4dd3-a6df-2ce46b77d442.webp","creator":"EdwarEG","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":27815,"messages":1043270,"created_at":"2024-05-30T05:46:01.589410+00:00"}